  "texts": [
    "Implementing CPS with beyond 5G technology will require substantial investments in research, development, and infrastructure.",
    "www.irjmets.com @International Research Journal of Modernization in Engineering, Technology and Science [2162] REGULATORY AND LEGAL COMPLIANCEComplying with a range of regulatory and legal requirements is also essential for CPS applications.",
    "These requirements include safety standards, privacy laws, and data protection regulations.",
    "Ensuring compliance with these requirements can be intricate, time-consuming, and add significant costs to the development and deployment of CPS.",
    "For instance, in the healthcare industry, CPS must adhere to the Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act, which imposes stringent rules for safeguarding patient data."
  ]
}